RAD_LOVS.LOV_QUERY: SELECT MIS_CODE, CODE_DESC from ((SELECT DISTINCT mis_code, code_desc FROM gltms_mis_code a, tltms_portfolio_expcode_master m, tltms_portfolio_expcode_detail d WHERE m.portfolio = d.portfolio AND d.expense_code = a.mis_code AND m.portfolio = ? AND active = 'A') UNION (SELECT DISTINCT mis_code, code_desc FROM gltms_mis_code a, tltms_portfolio_expcode_master m, tltms_portfolio_expcode_detail d, tltms_position_identifier e WHERE m.portfolio = d.portfolio AND m.portfolio = e.portfolio AND d.expense_code = a.mis_code AND e.position_identifier = ? AND active = 'A'))

RAD_DATASOURCES.RELATION_WITH_PARENT: LBTBS_LT_INTERFACE_BROWSER.BORR_REF_NO = LBTBS_SLT_EXCEPTION.BORROWER_REF_NO AND LBTBS_LT_INTERFACE_BROWSER.BORR_ESN = LBTBS_SLT_EXCEPTION.EVENT_SEQ_NO AND LBTBS_LT_INTERFACE_BROWSER.PART_REF_NO = LBTBS_SLT_EXCEPTION.PARTICIPANT_REF_NO AND LBTBS_LT_INTERFACE_BROWSER.PROCESS_SEQ_NO=LBTBS_SLT_EXCEPTION.PROCESS_SEQ_NO

RAD_LOVS.LOV_QUERY: select BORR_ESN from LBTBS_LT_INTERFACE_BROWSER where BORR_REF_NO = ?
select PART_REF_NO from LBTBS_LT_INTERFACE_BROWSER where BORR_REF_NO = ?
select PROCESS_SEQ_NO from LBTBS_LT_INTERFACE_BROWSER where BORR_REF_NO = ?
